  "texts": [
    "The expert name is set to \"Wikipedia\".",
    "In related work, Weller et al. (2023) measured LLM grounding to world knowledge.",
    "In order to measure how well an LLM's output was grounded to Wikipedia, they devised a metric: QUIP-score.",
    "This score is the character n-gram precision of the generated output compared to the source corpus.",
    "It is a useful metric in our case too, as we can measure how precisely each LLM's output is grounded in the given in-prompt knowledge."
